4. CLAUDE CODE TOOLING — Agents, skills, guardrails
================================================================================

### Agents created (.claude/agents/)

  batch-doctor.md
    Read-only health check of full Batch stack. Checks CEs, queue, recent
    failures, launch template UserData, S3 buckets, running instances,
    Nextflow logs. Outputs a status table with WARN/FAIL callouts.

  log-reader.md
    Parses .nextflow.log* files and fetches CloudWatch logs for failed Batch
    jobs. Produces a concise run report: succeeded/failed/aborted, timing,
    error messages.

### Skills created (.claude/skills/)

  deploy-stack.md
    Validates CFN template, deploys stack with all correct parameters, waits
    for completion, disables/re-enables CEs to re-validate. Shows diff first.

  preflight.md
    Pre-flight checklist before pipeline runs: CEs valid, queue enabled,
    launch template has stop-ecs guard, S3 reachable, no stuck jobs.

### Guardrails hook (.claude/hooks/guardrails.sh)

  PreToolUse hook configured in .claude/settings.json. Fires before every
  Bash, Write, and Edit call.

  Hard blocks (exit 2):
    - docker compose down -v, docker volume rm/prune, docker system prune
    - aws ec2 run-instances, aws ec2 request-spot-instances
    - aws batch update-compute-environment with maxvCpus > 64
    - aws cloudformation delete-stack
    - dd if=, fallocate, mkfs
    - rm -r outside the repo
    - git push --force to main/master, git reset --hard on main/master
    - Write to .env, credentials, *.key files
    - Write/Edit to paths outside repo (except ~/.claude/)

  Soft blocks (confirmation prompt):
    - nextflow run ... -profile aws

  Tested against 14 scenarios — all pass:
    docker compose down -v       → BLOCKED
    ls -la                       → allowed
    write /etc/passwd            ��� BLOCKED
    nextflow run -profile aws    → soft ask (permissionDecision: "ask")
    docker volume prune          → BLOCKED
    ec2 run-instances            → BLOCKED
    maxvCpus=256                 → BLOCKED
    maxvCpus=16                  → allowed
    cloudformation delete-stack  → BLOCKED
    git push --force main        → BLOCKED
    rm -rf /home/ubuntu/disk_dbs → BLOCKED
    rm -rf work/                 → allowed (inside repo)
    edit main.nf                 → allowed (inside repo)
    write .env                   → BLOCKED

